fdisk -l
    3  mkfs -t ext4 /dev/xvdf
    4  lsblk
    5  cd /mnt
    6  ls -ltr
    7  df -h
    8  mount /dev/xvdf /mnt
    9  df -h
   10  midir abc xyz prq
   11  mkdir abc xyz pqr
   12  ls -ltr
   13  cd abc
   14  touch a b c
   15  cd ..
   16  cd xy
   17  cd xyz
   18  ls -ltr
   19  df -h
   20  cd ..
   21  umount /dev/xvdf
   22  cd mnt
   23  df -h
   24  fdisk -l

At Volume 
 - Create Volume
 - Attach Volume
 - Make File system = mkfs
 - mount to it folder = mount
 - Add Data
 - Work complete, umount it
 - Volume Detach
 - Volume Delete
 so, it remove from instance.
